{"id":9380,"date":"2020-03-04T22:55:52","date_gmt":"2020-03-04T15:55:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/?p=9380"},"modified":"2020-03-10T10:07:21","modified_gmt":"2020-03-10T03:07:21","slug":"tim-hieu-quy-trinh-thiet-ke-logo-chuyen-nghiep","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tim-hieu-quy-trinh-thiet-ke-logo-chuyen-nghiep.html\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u quy tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_36 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">N\u1ed9i Dung<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><label for=\"item\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;width: 35px;height: 30px;justify-content: center;\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"item\"><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tim-hieu-quy-trinh-thiet-ke-logo-chuyen-nghiep.html\/#Quy_trinh_thiet_ke_logo_bao_gom_nhung_buoc_nao\" title=\"Quy tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo bao g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0o?\">Quy tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo bao g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0o?<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tim-hieu-quy-trinh-thiet-ke-logo-chuyen-nghiep.html\/#1_Lap_bang_dinh_huong_sang_tao\" title=\"1. L\u1eadp b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o\">1. L\u1eadp b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tim-hieu-quy-trinh-thiet-ke-logo-chuyen-nghiep.html\/#2_Tim_hieu_ki_luong_ve_doanh_nghiep\" title=\"2.\u00a0 T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u0129 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u1ec1 doanh nghi\u1ec7p\">2.\u00a0 T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u0129 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u1ec1 doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tim-hieu-quy-trinh-thiet-ke-logo-chuyen-nghiep.html\/#3_Nghien_cuu_cac_doanh_nghiep_cung_nganh\" title=\"3. Nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f9ng ng\u00e0nh\">3. Nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f9ng ng\u00e0nh<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tim-hieu-quy-trinh-thiet-ke-logo-chuyen-nghiep.html\/#4_Phac_thao_y_tuong_thiet_ke\" title=\"4. Ph\u00e1c th\u1ea3o \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf\">4. Ph\u00e1c th\u1ea3o \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tim-hieu-quy-trinh-thiet-ke-logo-chuyen-nghiep.html\/#5_Thuyet_trinh_y_tuong_logo\" title=\"5. Thuy\u1ebft tr\u00ecnh \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng logo\">5. Thuy\u1ebft tr\u00ecnh \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng logo<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tim-hieu-quy-trinh-thiet-ke-logo-chuyen-nghiep.html\/#6_Lap_cam_nang_thiet_ke_logo\" title=\"6. L\u1eadp c\u1ea9m nang thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo\">6. L\u1eadp c\u1ea9m nang thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><em><strong>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Logo<\/strong>\u00a0th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u cho c\u00f4ng ty, doanh nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 khi n\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. \u0110\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng sai s\u00f3t kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1edf n\u00ean chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u01a1n trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed3 h\u1ecda, c\u00e1c designer hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ea1o cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t\u00a0<strong>quy tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo<\/strong>\u00a0ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n.<\/em><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quy_trinh_thiet_ke_logo_bao_gom_nhung_buoc_nao\"><\/span><strong>Quy tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo bao g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0o?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Lap_bang_dinh_huong_sang_tao\"><\/span><strong><span id=\"1_Lp_bn_nh_hng_sng_to\">1. L\u1eadp b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i may r\u1ee7i. Do v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng khi b\u1ea1n g\u1ecdi t\u1edbi <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/\">Achaumedia<\/a> v\u00e0 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo cho c\u00f4ng ty, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n b\u1ea1n \u201cl\u00e0m m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i t\u1eadp v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0\u201d \u2013 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1n v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi thu th\u1eadp c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 so\u1ea1n s\u1eb5n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1ecdi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o (ho\u1eb7c creative brief). Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o n\u00e0y th\u00ec s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eabu ph\u00e1c th\u1ea3o logo n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p><strong>V\u1eady b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9434\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/quy-trinh-thiet-ke-logo.jpg\" alt=\"quy tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo\" width=\"700\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/quy-trinh-thiet-ke-logo.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/quy-trinh-thiet-ke-logo-300x145.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/quy-trinh-thiet-ke-logo-768x370.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>T\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y v\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y trong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft chi ti\u1ebft kh\u00e1c, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3i chung b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 doanh nghi\u1ec7p \/ th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u<\/li>\n<li>L\u0129nh v\u1ef1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \/ S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u2013 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5<\/li>\n<li>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng (T\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn \u2013 S\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh \u2013 Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ed1t l\u00f5i)<\/li>\n<li>Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau?<\/li>\n<li>M\u00f4 t\u1ea3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do h\u1ecd ch\u1ecdn th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/li>\n<li>Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ea7n truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i trong logo<\/li>\n<li>Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian<\/li>\n<li>C\u00e1c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u r\u00e0ng bu\u1ed9c kh\u00e1c<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Tim_hieu_ki_luong_ve_doanh_nghiep\"><\/span><strong><span id=\"2_Tm_hiu_k_lng_v_doanh_nghip\">2.\u00a0 T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u0129 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u1ec1 doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o (\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p b\u1edfi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng c\u00e1c c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n), gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac nh\u00f3m th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n d\u1ef1 \u00e1n ng\u1ed3i nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u l\u1ea1i n\u00f3. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp gi\u1eefa b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn Account (b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng) v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m h\u1ecda s\u1ef9 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng cung c\u1ea5p, l\u00e0m r\u00f5 v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu trong b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o.<\/p>\n<p>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp nh\u00f3m n\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin trong b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o n\u00f3 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0 h\u1eefu \u00edch.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Nghien_cuu_cac_doanh_nghiep_cung_nganh\"><\/span><strong><span id=\"3_Nghin_cu_cc_doanh_nghip_cng_ngnh\">3. Nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f9ng ng\u00e0nh<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecf qua. Vi\u1ec7c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u1ec1 ng\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng c\u0169ng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n doanh nghi\u1ec7p. Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9435\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/nghien-cuu-doi-thu-canh-tranh.jpg\" alt=\"thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo\" width=\"700\" height=\"393\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/nghien-cuu-doi-thu-canh-tranh.jpg 742w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/nghien-cuu-doi-thu-canh-tranh-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>V\u00ed d\u1ee5: c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p trong ng\u00e0nh c\u00f3 logo tr\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o? C\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1c ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng th\u01b0\u1eddng \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u00e1c m\u1ea7u xanh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng? C\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1c m\u1ea7u \u1ea5m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi ng\u00e0nh th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m? Logo c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t xi m\u0103ng th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 h\u00ecnh linh v\u1eadt? Li\u1ec7u ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p trong ng\u00e0nh hay v\u1eabn tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng quy \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0nh \u0111\u00f3? (v\u00ed d\u1ee5 m\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 tr\u1eafng l\u00e0 m\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0nh y t\u1ebf).<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Phac_thao_y_tuong_thiet_ke\"><\/span><strong><span id=\"4_Phc_tho_tng_thit_k\">4. Ph\u00e1c th\u1ea3o \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y, khi \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, c\u00e1c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 kinh doanh\u2026 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o ph\u00e1c th\u1ea3o ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf.<\/p>\n<p>T\u00f9y theo th\u00f3i quen, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u1ecda s\u1ef9 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1c th\u1ea3o \u0111en tr\u1eafng tr\u00ean gi\u1ea5y, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean m\u00e1y t\u00ednh. Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ph\u00e1c th\u1ea3o \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. Sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed7i h\u1ecda s\u1ef9 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn l\u1ecdc l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng hay v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9436\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/nguyen-tac-mot-thiet-ke-logo.jpg\" alt=\"ph\u00e1c th\u1ea3o \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo\" width=\"700\" height=\"424\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/nguyen-tac-mot-thiet-ke-logo.jpg 650w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/nguyen-tac-mot-thiet-ke-logo-300x182.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Ti\u1ebfp theo l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdp l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eedi cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Con s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t theo ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 4-5 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n. \u00cdt ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n qu\u00e1 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u qu\u00e1 c\u0169ng l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng th\u00eam ph\u00e2n v\u00e2n.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Thuyet_trinh_y_tuong_logo\"><\/span><strong><span id=\"5_Thuyt_trnh_tng_logo\">5. Thuy\u1ebft tr\u00ecnh \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng logo<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>M\u1ed7i m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m m\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi g\u1eafm trong \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn logo, Achau s\u1ebd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u00e0i thuy\u1ebft tr\u00ecnh \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng logo gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u00fd ngh\u0129a t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m. Thuy\u1ebft tr\u00ecnh \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng logo th\u01b0\u1eddng bao g\u1ed3m vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e2n t\u00edch \u00fd ngh\u0129a logo, ch\u1ec9 ra ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, ch\u1ec9 ra qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u1eeb tr\u1ef1c quan \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eebu t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f3a \u2026<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9437\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/unnamed-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"thuy\u1ebft tr\u00ecnh \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng logo\" width=\"700\" height=\"489\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/unnamed-1-1.jpg 512w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/unnamed-1-1-300x210.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00f4i khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0a logo v\u00e0o c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00e1c nhau, v\u00ed d\u1ee5 namecard, \u1ea5n ph\u1ea9m qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, bi\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng \u2026 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh m\u1eabu logo ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6_Lap_cam_nang_thiet_ke_logo\"><\/span><strong><span id=\"6_Lp_cm_nang_thit_k_logo\">6. L\u1eadp c\u1ea9m nang thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>C\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp theo khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo \u01b0ng \u00fd l\u00e0 bi\u00ean t\u1eadp n\u00f4i dung\u00a0<strong>c\u1ea9m nang h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng logo<\/strong>\u00a0(Logo Guidelines). C\u1ea9m nang n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap doanh nghi\u1ec7p \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng logo trong m\u1ecdi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng m\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh nh\u1ea5t qu\u00e1n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. C\u1ea9m nang logo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bao g\u1ed3m:\u00a0<em>logo, \u00fd ngh\u0129a logo, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 \u00f4 l\u01b0\u1edbi, font ch\u1eef v\u00e0 typo, m\u1ea7u s\u1eafc thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, logo \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng tr\u00ean c\u00e1c n\u1ec1n m\u1ea7u, c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u1ed1ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, logo v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan v\u1edbi c\u00e1c logo kh\u00e1c \u2026.<\/em><\/p>\n<p>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 <strong>quy tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo<\/strong> ,b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u s\u00e2u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1\u00a0quy tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u\u00a0chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p ho\u1eb7c kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng ngay d\u1ef1 \u00e1n\u00a0thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch li\u00ean h\u1ec7 qua <strong>Hotline: 09 3360 4283<\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Logo\u00a0th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u cho c\u00f4ng ty, doanh nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 khi n\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. \u0110\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng sai s\u00f3t kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1edf n\u00ean chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u01a1n trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c thi\u1ebft&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[94,51,52],"tags":[388],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Quy tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p | \u00c1 CH\u00c2U MEDIA<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"\u0110\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng sai s\u00f3t kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1edf... c\u00e1c designer hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ea1o cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t\u00a0quy tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo\u00a